metadata.title: Saanich Inlet Moored Buoy Data, 1999
metadata.description: Chlorophyll, phytoplankton, and nutrient data collected in Saanich Inlet in spring-summer, 1999.  Data were collected to support MEOS buoy data (see Marine Ecosystem ObServatory entry) moored in Saanich Inlet.
keywords: South Inner Coast (Johnstone, Georgia, JDF, inlets and passages)
